data.description: Welcome to this unique property situated on three spacious lots, providing ample space to build multiple properties in a desirable location. This property presents an exciting opportunity for developers, investors, or those looking to create their own dream estate.  The existing property features numerous updates, including an updated kitchen, modern bathrooms, and new flooring throughout. The home is equipped with an interior sprinkler system. The open floor plan of the main living area provides a welcoming space for family and friends to gather, with plenty of natural light that pours in through the large windows.   This property's location is ideal, situated in a desirable area that is close to schools, shopping, and entertainment. The three lots offer endless possibilities for new construction, whether it be creating multiple homes, a larger estate, or a mixed-use development.  Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity to own a property with endless possibilities for development in a prime location. Schedule a viewing today and explore the endless possibilities for this fantastic property
